    90	Q: Why doesn't Partition Resizer look a bit more fancy?
    91	A: Partition Resizer is designed to run in ANY PC, including the old XTs and
    92	monochrome PCs. Using graphics would make it difficult, and sometimes
    93	impossible to run on such systems. There are many people who still have such
    94	machines, and I have received messages from some of them who used Partition 
    95	Resizer. I'm thinking of adding some text windows and colors to the program,
    96	but there are more importat things to do first.
